




{"id":15714,"date":"2024-06-10T09:59:59","date_gmt":"2024-06-10T02:59:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=15714"},"modified":"2024-06-10T09:59:59","modified_gmt":"2024-06-10T02:59:59","slug":"bi-quyet-cho-nhung-gio-hoc-hung-khoi-va-hieu-qua-voi-man-hinh-tuong-tac-inno","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/bi-quyet-cho-nhung-gio-hoc-hung-khoi-va-hieu-qua-voi-man-hinh-tuong-tac-inno\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u00ed quy\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNO"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi <\/span><b>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNO<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> &#8211; c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft! H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u00f9ng INNO nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>M\u1edf ra th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111en, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNO v\u1edbi <\/span><b>ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 4K<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, video s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea3nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp gi\u00fap<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u1eafm ch\u00ecm v\u00e0o b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean &#8220;c\u00f3 h\u1ed3n&#8221; h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 3D, m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng, hay nh\u1eefng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n trong s\u00e1ch v\u1edf, m\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean tr\u1ef1c quan v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15715\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-INNO.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"598\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-INNO.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-INNO-602x400.webp 602w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-INNO-768x510.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-INNO-600x399.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>K\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ham h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi <\/span><b>b\u00fat vi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng minh<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> bi\u1ebfn <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> th\u00e0nh &#8220;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">h\u1ecda s\u0129<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8221; v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1ebd, vi\u1ebft, ch\u00fa th\u00edch tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">INNO cho ph\u00e9p <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 tay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh, tham gia th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn nh\u00f3m, hay gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng nhau v\u1edbi <\/span><b>t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng t\u01b0 duy s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u00f3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u phong c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thay v\u00ec ghi ch\u00e9p th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">c\u00e1c em <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi ch\u00fa tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nhau<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin nhanh ch\u00f3ng, so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9 trong t\u00edch t\u1eafc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1eadp tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211;<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u00a0 <\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u01b0u tr\u1eef b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng, ghi ch\u00fa v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi v\u00e0i thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><b>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng INNO chinh ph\u1ee5c tri th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi!<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNO &#8211; c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft! H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u00f9ng INNO nh\u00e9! M\u1edf&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15715,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false